data: {"type": "text-delta", "id": "7170f0f0-4d3e-4af7-960c-c3e190d216bd", "delta": "To check if a systemd service is active on RHEL 9:\n\n*   **Script-friendly (yes/no):**  \n    `systemctl is-active <service_name>`\n*   **Detailed status:**  \n    `systemctl status <service_name>`\n\nReplace `<service_name>` with the actual service (e.g., `sshd`, `httpd`)."}

